            </p>

            <h2 class="text-justify">Inquire about references</h2>

            <p class="text-justify">Of course, no one will accuse them of being a bad agent with a history of failed excursions. Clients in the past, on the other hand, can speak volumes. You'll get a far more objective assessment of their strengths and flaws here. You'll be able to obtain a clear idea of how the process will progress in the long run. Do they work well in groups? What if you get into problems when traveling abroad and require assistance? Get to know them better with people who have already received their services. </p>

